00:00:02,939 --> 00:00:03,983
The boy that Ms. Kurumi Shodo

2
00:00:04,239 --> 00:00:07,987
"Kurumi Shodo (39)" -befriended at the beach 30 years ago,

3
00:00:07,987 --> 00:00:10,839
