5
00:00:13,639 --> 00:00:15,339
Kurumi says that the lottery ticket she happened to buy

6
00:00:15,339 --> 00:00:17,139
was a winning ticket for 1 billion yen

7
00:00:17,139 --> 00:00:19,239
and she wants to give it to the boy who saved her.

8
00:00:19,239 --> 00:00:22,001
So, she contacted TV stations and magazines.

9
00:00:22,239 --> 00:00:25,139
The clues are her memory of the summer days

10
00:00:25,139 --> 00:00:27,439
and the large scar that the boy got

11
00:00:27,439 --> 00:00:28,839
when he saved her from the accident.

12
00:00:30,009 --> 00:00:33,439
Two men appear when she calls out for the boy.

13
00:00:33,439 --> 00:00:36,015
Mr. Ryuhei Kusumoto has a large scar on his back

14
00:00:36,239 --> 00:00:38,039
and Mr. Sogo Banba has a scar on his chest.

15
00:00:38,039 --> 00:00:41,539
Both scars are large, extending in one straight line.

16
00:00:41,539 --> 00:00:44,023
In order to discern which is the real man

17
00:00:44,239 --> 00:00:46,839
we all go to visit the Shodo residence but,

18
00:00:46,839 --> 00:00:51,239
there we find the officers of the First Investigation Division

19
00:00:51,239 --> 00:00:52,639
secretly staking out in pursuit of a killer

20
00:00:52,639 --> 00:00:54,839
whose time is about to expire.

21
00:00:54,839 --> 00:00:58,739
That culprit also has a straight lined scar on his body.

22
00:00:59,739 --> 00:01:02,041
However, we also find that

23
00:01:02,041 --> 00:01:03,639
the butler at the Shodo residence,

24
00:01:03,639 --> 00:01:06,339
Mr. Taisuke Hoya has a scar on his back.

25
00:01:06,339 --> 00:01:10,049
Who on earth is the "boy of her memory"?

26
00:01:12,051 --> 00:01:14,053
Love is eternal, labyrinths are mysterious.

27
00:01:14,053 --> 00:01:16,439
Saturday nights are for mystery.

28
00:01:16,439 --> 00:01:18,439
With the deadline approaching, a first love comes to light.

29
00:01:18,439 --> 00:01:20,939
The case of the scar takes an unexpected turn!

30
00:01:20,939 --> 00:01:22,539
He sees through the one and only truth.

31
00:01:22,539 --> 00:01:24,339
A child in appearance with the I.Q. of an adult.

32
00:01:24,339 --> 00:01:26,065
No case is left unsolved with Detective Conan.

33
00:03:08,167 --> 00:03:12,988
"The Scar that Invokes the Past"

34
00:03:14,888 --> 00:03:16,175
No way.

35
00:03:16,175 --> 00:03:18,988
The butler had a scar on his back too?

36
00:03:18,988 --> 00:03:22,788
Yes. Although unlike Mr. Kusumoto and Banba's scar,

37
00:03:22,788 --> 00:03:26,488
his scar was smaller that had only about 15 cm.

38
00:03:26,488 --> 00:03:29,088
There's a chance that Hoya the butler,

39
00:03:29,088 --> 00:03:32,488
may turn out to be the murderer too.

40
00:03:32,488 --> 00:03:33,488
Why?

41
00:03:33,488 --> 00:03:36,588
Isn't the scar on the murderer a big one too?

42
00:03:36,588 --> 00:03:38,197
Well, when the Superintendent slashed

43
00:03:38,197 --> 00:03:40,588
the killer and wounded him,

44
00:03:40,588 --> 00:03:43,488
he was dazed out,

45
00:03:43,488 --> 00:03:45,388
so it could be that he doesn't remember

46
00:03:45,388 --> 00:03:47,588
the accurate length of the scar.

47
00:03:47,588 --> 00:03:49,588
Besides, it seems as if that murderer

48
00:03:49,588 --> 00:03:52,488
is very cautious too.

49
00:03:53,888 --> 00:03:56,888
After that killer was slashed by the Superintendent,

50
00:03:56,888 --> 00:03:58,888
he fled by car,

51
00:03:58,888 --> 00:04:01,188
but when the car was found later,

52
