The sheet covering the driver's seat was torn off,

54
00:04:08,988 --> 00:04:11,888
so the killer probably wiped away his prints that were in the car

55
00:04:11,888 --> 00:04:14,233
after tearing off the part where his blood stains were.

56
00:04:14,488 --> 00:04:19,788
But, what makes you say that the butler may be the killer?

57
00:04:19,788 --> 00:04:21,388
If the guy is cautious,

58
00:04:21,388 --> 00:04:23,988
it's hard to believe that he would publicize himself,

59
00:04:23,988 --> 00:04:27,088
even for the sake of receiving money.

60
00:04:27,088 --> 00:04:30,249
After all, luminol reaction which usually detects

61
00:04:30,249 --> 00:04:32,588
the traces of blood even after being wiped off,

62
00:04:32,588 --> 00:04:35,688
wasn't detected.

63
00:04:35,688 --> 00:04:38,257
The scars of the three men.

64
00:04:38,257 --> 00:04:41,188
There's big one on Mr. Kusumoto's back

65
00:04:41,188 --> 00:04:43,888
and Mr. Banba's chest.

66
00:04:43,888 --> 00:04:46,788
On Mr. Hoya's back there is a small scar.

67
00:04:47,788 --> 00:04:50,588
Mr. Kusumoto used to be thin when he was a child

68
00:04:50,588 --> 00:04:53,588
and, Mr. Banba used to be a bookworm.

69
00:04:53,588 --> 00:04:55,088
The boy in her memory

70
00:04:55,088 --> 00:04:56,988
was knowledgeable of the sea and fish.

71
00:04:56,988 --> 00:04:59,888
His favourite drink is ginger ale.

72
00:04:59,888 --> 00:05:03,088
His favourite food are sushi and fried noodles.

73
00:05:03,088 --> 00:05:05,588
He is a very honest person.

74
00:05:05,588 --> 00:05:08,588
The nickname his classmates named him

75
00:05:08,588 --> 00:05:09,888
was Gari.

76
00:05:11,988 --> 00:05:12,988
Yes.

77
00:05:14,588 --> 00:05:17,788
How is the investigation coming along?

78
00:05:17,788 --> 00:05:20,988
Well... Nothing definite has come up yet.

79
00:05:20,988 --> 00:05:22,301
I see.

80
00:05:22,301 --> 00:05:25,188
Well, there's still more time.

81
00:05:25,188 --> 00:05:27,888
A slight meal is ready, so you can eat if you like.

82
00:05:27,888 --> 00:05:30,088
Light meal?

83
00:05:30,088 --> 00:05:33,188
Let me guess, it's...

84
00:05:33,188 --> 00:05:34,688
sushi?

85
00:05:34,688 --> 00:05:37,788
Yes, amazing how you know.

86
00:05:37,788 --> 00:05:39,788
Well, you see...

87
00:05:39,788 --> 00:05:42,321
I've got a secret to tell you.

88
00:05:43,788 --> 00:05:45,388
A little more below.

89
00:05:50,329 --> 00:05:52,331
What're they talking about?

90
00:05:53,688 --> 00:05:56,335
Will you please do so then?

91
00:05:56,335 --> 00:05:57,288
Okay.

92
00:05:58,337 --> 00:06:00,788
How surprising, though.

93
00:06:00,788 --> 00:06:04,343
I thought that you were just a short high school boy

