95
00:06:08,347 --> 00:06:11,888
But, you're still such a little boy.

96
00:06:11,888 --> 00:06:15,888
It's as if Sherlock Holmes is pretending to be a child.

97
00:06:15,888 --> 00:06:17,488
Really?

98
00:06:17,488 --> 00:06:21,088
I can see what normal people can't.

99
00:06:22,361 --> 00:06:25,488
I'll be waiting in my room, then.

100
00:06:25,488 --> 00:06:27,888
I'll leave the rest up to you.

101
00:06:29,788 --> 00:06:31,088
Mr. Detective.

102
00:06:31,088 --> 00:06:32,888
Yes.

103
00:06:37,688 --> 00:06:39,488
Super premium sushi for sure.

104
00:06:43,788 --> 00:06:45,688
Why don't you have some too, butler?

105
00:06:45,688 --> 00:06:49,088
Kurumi said for you to eat together with us.

106
00:06:49,088 --> 00:06:50,389
Yes.

107
00:06:50,588 --> 00:06:51,888
I guess so.

108
00:06:58,788 --> 00:07:02,401
Natural stuff is good after all.

109
00:07:02,401 --> 00:07:04,688
No, this is artificially bred fish.

110
00:07:04,688 --> 00:07:06,188
