00:15:20,488 --> 00:15:21,988
How about it?

285
00:15:21,988 --> 00:15:23,888
Yes.

286
00:15:23,888 --> 00:15:25,388
If I remember correctly,

287
00:15:25,388 --> 00:15:28,288
it was a tune that was popular about 20 years ago.

288
00:15:28,288 --> 00:15:30,288
You're not lying, are you?

289
00:15:30,288 --> 00:15:31,488
No.

290
00:15:31,488 --> 00:15:33,988
Superintendent.

291
00:15:33,988 --> 00:15:36,588
Popular 20 years ago.

292
00:15:36,588 --> 00:15:39,488
That's the tune of the serial killer.

293
00:15:48,208 --> 00:15:51,408
Ryuhei Kusumoto, age 42.

294
00:15:51,408 --> 00:15:53,808
Around the time the incident occurred 15 years ago,

295
00:15:53,808 --> 00:15:56,708
he seems to have been abroad home-staying.

296
00:15:56,708 --> 00:15:58,708
This has been confirmed,

297
00:15:58,708 --> 00:16:01,308
so I guess he could be cleared from the list of suspects.

298
00:16:01,308 --> 00:16:02,408
I see.

299
00:16:03,408 --> 00:16:06,108
He seems to have met the man with the scar on his back at a sauna

300
00:16:06,108 --> 00:16:10,008
just before he left to go abroad to home-stay.

301
00:16:10,008 --> 00:16:12,108
He seems to have had a towel over his head,

