303
00:16:15,208 --> 00:16:16,408
The man seems to have laughed and said,

304
00:16:16,408 --> 00:16:18,957
"This scar was made on my back 5 years ago

305
00:16:18,957 --> 00:16:20,408
by the police and is a crest of courage.

306
00:16:20,408 --> 00:16:23,408
You want to have one like this too?"

307
00:16:23,408 --> 00:16:24,963
Is anyone at that sauna?

308
00:16:24,963 --> 00:16:28,967
Officer Sato and Takagi are staking out there right now.

309
00:16:28,967 --> 00:16:31,808
Tell them to stay on their guard.

310
00:16:31,808 --> 00:16:32,971
Yes, sir.

311
00:16:32,971 --> 00:16:36,708
He's a vicious killer who killed a total of 3 people,

312
00:16:36,708 --> 00:16:40,208
2 people 20 years ago and 1 person 15 years ago.

313
00:16:41,408 --> 00:16:43,608
No, there's one more.

314
00:16:43,608 --> 00:16:45,308
Did you forget?

315
00:16:46,308 --> 00:16:48,708
I'd never forget

316
00:16:48,708 --> 00:16:50,989
about Superintendent Morimura who died on duty

317
00:16:50,989 --> 00:16:53,308
because of that incident.

318
00:16:53,308 --> 00:16:56,408
After all, he's the one who taught me all I need to know

319
00:16:56,408 --> 00:16:58,208
about being a police detective.

320
00:17:04,708 --> 00:17:07,908
Superintendent Morimura.

321
00:17:07,908 --> 00:17:09,508
After you died on duty,

322
00:17:09,508 --> 00:17:11,908
you were specially promoted 2 ranks,

323
00:17:11,908 --> 00:17:14,408
and I've finally caught up to your rank now.

324
00:17:14,408 --> 00:17:16,408
But, I still don't understand

325
00:17:16,408 --> 00:17:19,017
the meaning of the words you said back then.

326
00:17:20,408 --> 00:17:24,208
Matsumoto, there's some meaning

327
00:17:24,208 --> 00:17:28,208
behind the tune that... that guy is whistling.

328
00:17:28,208 --> 00:17:31,029
I'm dead sure... there's something.

329
00:17:32,008 --> 00:17:36,608
What on earth could there be, Morimura?

330
00:17:37,608 --> 00:17:40,208
So there was nothing after all.

331
00:17:40,208 --> 00:17:41,408
Nothing at all.

332
00:17:41,408 --> 00:17:43,408
Well, it can't be helped.

333
00:17:43,408 --> 00:17:45,808
It's an incident that happened 15 years ago.

334
00:17:45,808 --> 00:17:47,045
I guess so.

