340
00:17:56,708 --> 00:17:58,708
That's right.

341
00:17:58,708 --> 00:18:02,208
Why don't you invite Officer Chiba and go there with him?

342
00:18:02,208 --> 00:18:04,408
I'll go, alone.

343
00:18:05,508 --> 00:18:07,708
Did you ask me to come with you?

344
00:18:07,708 --> 00:18:10,108
Of course!

345
00:18:10,108 --> 00:18:12,108
Then, why don't we do this?

346
00:18:12,108 --> 00:18:13,508
If we get to arrest this serial killer

347
00:18:13,508 --> 00:18:15,508
before the expiration date,

348
00:18:15,508 --> 00:18:18,108
let's go to a hot spring together.

349
00:18:18,108 --> 00:18:20,308
But, we've only got three more days to go.

350
00:18:20,308 --> 00:18:22,708
Take me to a hot spring.

351
00:18:22,708 --> 00:18:23,908
You know what...

352
00:18:23,908 --> 00:18:25,508
I wonder, is it okay?

353
00:18:26,508 --> 00:18:29,908
For officers to be acting lovey-dovey on duty.

354
00:18:29,908 --> 00:18:33,091
Oh, no. We're not acting lovey-dovey.

355
00:18:33,091 --> 00:18:35,108
We're questioning the people around here...

356
00:18:36,108 --> 00:18:38,808
Don't tell the children what you don't have to.

357
00:18:38,808 --> 00:18:40,408
I know.

358
00:18:40,408 --> 00:18:44,008
If I put together the details of the incident that was aired on TV

359
00:18:44,008 --> 00:18:47,105
and what Superintendent Matsumoto said,

360
